    <item>
      <title>以色列军队进入黎巴嫩，与真主党发生冲突</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/israeli-troops-move-into-lebanon-extending-fight-with-hezbollah</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列派遣军队进入黎巴嫩南部，加强了其长达数周的行动，严重削弱了伊朗支持的真主党武装组织，并增加了爆发更大范围地区冲突的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/israeli-troops-move-into-lebanon-extending-fight-with-hezbollah</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 07:10:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本首相石破茂就任，内阁暗示延续性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/japan-s-ishiba-set-to-become-prime-minister-in-parliament-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石破茂被任命为日本新任首相，并公布了内阁阵容，管理国家的压力转移到了这位政治理想主义者的肩上，他在漫长的职业生涯中大部分时间都在从旁批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/japan-s-ishiba-set-to-become-prime-minister-in-parliament-vote</guid>
